<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>TulipParty</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/aero.css">
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>TulipParty</h1>
    <div class="header-links">
      <a href="/chat" class="create-button">Live Chat</a>
      <a href="/favorites" class="create-button"><i class="fas fa-star"></i> Favorites</a>
      <a href="/friends" class="create-button"><i class="fas fa-user-friends"></i> Friends</a>
      <a href="/create-category" class="create-button">New Category</a>
      <a href="/create" class="create-button">New Post</a>
    </div>
  </header>
  
  <div class="marquee-container">
    <div class="marquee-content">
      <span>Welcome to TulipParty - Stickers coming soon!1! - Pick a category below - Agartha never died - </span>
      <span>Welcome to TulipParty - Stickers coming soon!1! - Pick a category below - Agartha never died - </span>
      <span>Welcome to TulipParty - Frick sticky keys - Pick a category below - Sharing is caring - </span>
      <span>Welcome to TulipParty - Frick sticky keys - Pick a category below - Sharing is caring - </span>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <main class="categories-container">
    <h2>Categories</h2>
    
    <% if (categories && categories.length > 0) { %>
      <div class="category-grid">
        <% categories.forEach(category => { %>
          <div class="category-card">
            <h3><a href="/category/<%= category.id %>"><%= category.name %></a></h3>
            <div class="category-meta">
              <span class="post-count"><%= category.post_count %> posts</span>
              <span class="creator">by <%= category.creator_name %></span>
            </div>
            <p class="category-desc"><%= category.description %></p>
          </div>
        <% }) %>
      </div>
    <% } else { %>
      <p class="no-categories">No categories found. Create one!</p>
    <% } %>
  </main>
  
  <div class="marquee-container bottom-marquee">
    <div class="marquee-content reverse">
      <span>TulipParty - 4chan? nah. - dreadsu free zone - find all the easter eggs! - </span>
      <span>TulipParty - 4chan? nah. - dreadsu free zone - find all the easter eggs! - </span>
      <span>TulipParty - JOIN OUR LIVE CHAT! - dreadsu free zone - easter egg one: ↑ ← → ↓ ↓ - </span>
      <span>TulipParty - JOIN OUR LIVE CHAT! - dreadsu free zone - easter egg one: ↑ ← → ↓ ↓ - </span>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <footer>
    <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> TulipParty - wowowowowo</p>
  </footer>
  <script src="/js/aeroEasterEgg.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/signupKeySequence.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
